1
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:04,440
According to regulations,

2
00:01:04,440 --> 00:01:07,400
the thickness of the car's bottom steel plate must be less than two millimeters.

3
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:08,080
Otherwise, it is prone to

4
00:01:08,080 --> 00:01:10,160
catching fire due to stones on the road.

5
00:01:10,160 --> 00:01:11,880
According to my investigation,

6
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:14,400
it is precisely because Mr. Li cut corners on the steel plates

7
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:17,400
that many TG300 race cars caught fire spontaneously.

8
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:20,320
Mr. Li,

9
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:22,360
do you have anything else to say?

10
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:22,920
I...

11
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:24,490
I am innocent, Chairman Gu.

12
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:25,440
This...

13
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:27,200
Someone is definitely trying to frame me.

14
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,440
You can't pass the buck

15
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:29,200
that easily.

16
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:30,360
Take him away.

17
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:31,570
Chairman Gu.

18
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,280
Chairman Gu!

19
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,280
I know I was wrong.

20
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:34,690
Give me another chance.

21
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:35,560
Chairman Gu!

22
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,400
Chairman Gu!

23
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,160
Chairman,

24
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:39,200
we have already reached an agreement

25
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,080
with all the dealers.

26
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:42,880
They will continue to sell TG new energy race cars.

27
00:01:42,960 --> 00:01:44,820
The crisis is resolved this time.

28
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,940
You made a great contribution this time.

29
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:53,400
I won't mistreat you.

30
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:55,800
Even if Haoran wakes up,

31
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:56,770
you can still

32
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:59,400
stay in the Gu Group as a senior executive.

33
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,160
No need.

34
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,920
Looking too much like Young Master Gu might not be a good thing.

35
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:05,980
I will leave on my own when he wakes up.

36
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,540
Thank you, sir.

37
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,320
This kid is not bad.

38
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,760
I wasn't wrong about him.

39
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:25,000
Today is April 20, 2020.

40
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,480
I am Chen Zixi.

41
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,650
Ye Lan, the owner of Lan Bar,

42
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:31,800
may hold behind-the-scenes info about the TG project.

43
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,400
She finally agreed to meet me

44
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:36,130
and said she has important info to reveal.

45
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:44,160
Shiqi,

46
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:45,720
look into this Ye Lan.

47
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:46,200
Okay.

48
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,320
Ye Lan is the owner of Lan Bar.

49
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:55,079
She was once the manager of the Qiyun Racing Team

50
00:02:55,079 --> 00:02:56,160
and led the team

51
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:58,760
to win the championship of the Longguo Grand Prix.

52
00:02:58,760 --> 00:02:59,960
After the team disbanded,

53
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,640
she opened a bar called Lan.

54
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:05,280
She profits from selling racing intel.

55
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,940
Maybe from this Ye Lan,

56
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,090
we can get some useful info.

57
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:29,960
Hello.

58
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:31,520
Hello.

59
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,280
Is your boss here?

60
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,360
Master Gu.

61
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:22,600
What brings you here?

62
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:25,740
She actually knows Master Gu.

63
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:28,770
It seems this boss is indeed quite something.

64
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:32,000
You

65
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,040
know me?

66
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:44,320
With Master Gu's reputation in the racing world,

67
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,380
it would be hard for me, Ye Lan,

68
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,720
not to know you.

69
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,040
Hello.

70
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,360
The person in this photo,

71
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,170
you know him, right?

72
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:01,320
Yes.

73
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:04,020
She bought intel from me three years ago.

74
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:04,740
What intel?

75
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:06,720
Sorry.

76
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:09,080
Although I am an information broker,

77
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:11,010
I have basic professional ethics.

78
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:13,960
I cannot reveal any customer's information.

79
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:16,520
Even if a charming handsome boy like you

80
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,480
begs me.

81
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:23,490
What if I want the same intel as her?

82
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,640
Playing smart.

83
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:31,060
One piece of intel can only be sold to one person.

84
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:33,560
Then I want the intel on Chen Zixi's murder.

85
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,760
This intel

86
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,180
is very expensive.

87
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:36,770
How much?

88
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,400
I don't want money.

89
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:43,720
I want you.

90
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:46,960
Boss Ye.

91
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,200
I sell my skills, not my body.

92
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:50,840
Interesting.

93
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:53,960
I heard that recently,

94
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:57,250
Young Master Gu showed off his driving skills

95
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,760
and stole the spotlight.

96
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,720
Since you want to sell your skills,

97
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:04,520
then show me your driving skills.

98
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:06,160
If I'm satisfied,

99
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:08,980
I'll give you this information for free.

100
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,200
Deal.

101
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,490
I'm good at this.

102
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:14,440
Don't celebrate just yet.

103
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,080
The rules

104
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:26,760
are made by me.

105
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,440
I haven't been to

106
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:38,520
the top of Wutong Mountain for half a year.

107
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,120
Tonight,

108
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:41,500
take me there to see the stars.

109
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:43,680
You want me to drive you up the mountain?

110
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,280
Exactly.

111
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:48,720
The mountain roads of Wutong Mountain are notoriously winding.

112
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:51,210
You must get me up there within 20 minutes.

113
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:52,400
During this time,

114
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:56,560
not a single drop of red wine can be spilled from the glass.

115
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,530
How about it?

116
00:06:57,960 --> 00:06:58,820
A piece of cake.

117
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,420
I've always been a steady driver.

118
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,460
I'm looking forward to it.

119
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,240
Sit tight.

120
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:08,160
Start.

121
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,600
Remember,

122
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,760
not a single drop of wine can be spilled.

123
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:31,490
Don't worry.

124
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,520
My AE86,

125
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:33,940
I absolutely trust it.

126
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:48,320
Not bad, kid.

127
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:51,080
Driving on winding roads at this speed,

128
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,560
and the wine didn't spill.

129
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,850
As long as Boss Ye is satisfied.

130
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:03,320
If you exceed the time limit,

131
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:05,380
you still won't get the information.

132
00:08:07,440 --> 00:08:08,480
There are three minutes left.

133
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,210
That's enough to reach the top.

134
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:04,600
As far as I know,

135
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,720
it's a dead end ahead.

136
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:09,130
Are you sure you want to take this road?

137
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:11,440
You'll know in a minute.

138
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:00,700
We're here.

139
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:02,400
Not bad.

140
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:04,500
19 minutes and 35 seconds.

141
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:05,920
It seems

142
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:07,850
my performance passed.

143
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:08,560
Of course.

144
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,320
You truly live up to the name of the once-famous

145
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,640
genius racer,

146
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:14,920
He Nan.
